{"name": "interface-gen", "metadata": {"name": "interface-gen", "version": "0.0.21", "classifiers": ["Development Status :: 4 - Beta", "License :: OSI Approved :: Apache Software License", "Operating System :: POSIX :: Linux", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3", "Topic :: File Formats"], "home_page": null, "license": null, "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["asn1tools", "attrs", "avro", "avrotize", "azure-core", "azure-identity", "azure-kusto-data", "bitstruct", "certifi", "cffi", "charset-normalizer", "cryptography", "fastavro", "flake8", "idna", "ijson", "install-jdk", "jsoncomparison", "jsonpath-ng", "jsonpointer", "jsonschema-specifications", "jsonschema", "lark", "mccabe", "msal-extensions", "msal", "numpy", "packaging", "ply", "portalocker", "pyarrow", "pycodestyle", "pycparser", "pyflakes", "pyjwt", "pyparsing", "python-dateutil", "referencing", "requests", "rpds-py", "six", "typing-extensions", "urllib3"], "summary": "Define data format schemas once and generate code for multiple languages and serialization frameworks.", "upload_time": 1733370481}, "documentation": ["# Interface Generator\n\nWrite your protocol specifications in a single language (Avro IDL) and\nautomatically generate schema definitions, code, and documentation for multiple\nlanguages and serialization frameworks, including:\n\n- Protobuf (proto3)\n- Apache Avro Schema (.avsc)\n- JSON schema\n- XML schema\n- SQL DDL (create table)\n- .. and of the other formats supported by [Avrotize](https://github.com/clemensv/avrotize).\n\n## Quick Start\n\n1. Create a virtual environment (optional but recommended), and activate it:\n\n```\npython -m venv venv\nsource venv/bin/activate\n\n```\n\n2. Install the package:\n\n```\npython -m pip install interface-gen\n```\n\n3. Set up your protocol definitions and output directory.\n\n```\nmkdir -p my-protocols/v1.0\nmkdir my-output\n```\n\nPlace your Avro IDL definition files (.avdl)  in `my-protocols/v1.0`\n\n4. Run the generator:\n\n```\nifgen -i -p my-protocols -o my-output\n```\n\n## More Details\n\nFor more details see the source code docs:\n\n- Python [interface\\_gen/README.md](https://github.com/getditto/interface_gen/blob/main/README.md)\n- Main [README.md](https://github.com/getditto/interface-gen/blob/main/README.md)\n- The [code repostitory](https://github.com/getditto/interface-gen)\n\n"], "modules": [{"name": "interface_gen.toolchain", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "interface_gen.toolchain.script_dir", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": {"name": "Path", "xref": {"fqname": "pathlib.Path", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "interface_gen.toolchain.download_file", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "url", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "out_dir", "type": {"name": "Path", "xref": {"fqname": "pathlib.Path", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "interface_gen.toolchain.avro_jar", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "version", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "Path", "xref": {"fqname": "pathlib.Path", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "interface_gen.toolchain.find_java", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "root", "type": {"name": "Path", "xref": {"fqname": "pathlib.Path", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "Path | None", "xref": null, "params": null}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "interface_gen.toolchain.ensure_jre", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": {"name": "Path | None", "xref": null, "params": null}, "documentation": ["Ensure that JRE is installed, and return its path. "]}, {"name": "interface_gen.toolchain.install_avro_tools", "asynchronous": false,